# 蒙文读音输入方法

蒙文读音输入方法是1988年着手开发，1990年开始应用于北大方正排版系统蒙古文版的输入方法，至今已有30多年的应用历史。文后附件为1991年5月收编入第五届全国少数民族语言文字信息处理论文集的《蒙文读音输入方法》截图。



本文一是精炼介绍原《蒙文读音输入方法》，二是介绍使用《传统蒙古文信息交换与处理字形字符编码字符集》实现蒙古文万码系统平台后，蒙文读音输入方法的变化内容。



## 一、原《蒙文读音输入方法》精炼



蒙文读音输入法是把蒙文按书面语的读音一个音对应在一个键位上，共用38个键位输入传统蒙古文文字的输入方法。

1.用38键a,e,E,i,q,v,o,u,n,N, b, p, h, H,g,G, m, l, s,x,t,T, d, D, c, j, y,Y, r,R, w, f, k, C, z, _（下划线）,'（单撇）,-（减号）。代表蒙文![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdwSvdaPib7qrMV8QwLsC0afqicUwPicibnoM3ZONklzFlaVGpXia0lIt1blw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdgt7lxoiaIOdRibxRNicgbq26Mias5xT7ecXky9fL71oPz2IjpWvnWGdPyw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdqpylbcUtquSUYB9vXv0yya69vlgmaice7odcUEbnVrwGib3xPPZlV5ZA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdm3It6yr0WOrhFsETY3CdRABvb6ulMPoibdvNqpsXdBkgFDydL3C9ibXg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdm3It6yr0WOrhFsETY3CdRABvb6ulMPoibdvNqpsXdBkgFDydL3C9ibXg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCd9qhMy2EGUKrsIThLBgr9v6KeOxZhjHpt7bxgJyMHYARXd2dC3YicPiaw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdwztiawTiaCdia7XNWNDX19ic4hvTPLuEqXRBGusxIHcDK4FCFQPibH0T3HQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdsc5nDejnnYXn60z8R7BSB1oRyquDf01nTXPddufib8ZgdVY39mKByFw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCd7CRHb4VpPUwfvScXWzbib0HbKueZ5ofd6Z85CiciaVSdz72XR2XwI6qSg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdwmMibiaztnOpPbfzPicjyjEq3C5BBKicncTI0OCdqOu6pLDdNOeZMUOicBQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdAiabcVJFjCDNfS59sby0FRvntnmxyy3dE70iczy396D5BNGJdpYDMDJw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1) ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdgjsmNamgp2KYCqvbwY3z5IjQt4tMkD4odlubJBRpFMeXC2Ec1F1jbw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdTSCyjQ5Ew5hTunyHXSXlPiaRdHIxpGEibmEa2qHtkOIKwDqy3R3krxPQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdrsIzPLvM078jUibvSYvBPgaaHE31OVpyibpEcicIvUUmia0Y3qGQeANjYQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdpYmZqNWDBWf6icrbdGwrGpDjMgashvsI9glibZBuF8H5yNQ9D1GqyI6A/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdfatFRwDsEh5lK7xjeXUSBFdGIZIBP1qiaK7tI9IF0ichxwv8fNDfQtDA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入，称这38个字符为蒙文读音字符（蒙音字符）。组合键ng,lh,zh,ch,_a代表蒙文![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdzI2J8GzfjhYCiaXdcEoM7XWXMqSvUTKcvyE6XNvp3NsK2d52neTIn4A/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCddiaUpcicZUicF4fJBC2nVnEeViczGEE4rgVpuDxfZYzSoKSOra9FwXYvHw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCd9XXBNllrr83j96AGkpas3J9HQuOLEBUKqqRDIonjDnzVaeeVtzCdOQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdeOEL5AlLR8jWeYxkD0jvHKTc4RysibjA7iaOZ7VlIAXPnIVHyicRYt6Qg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdZcKyKC5K2C7uwEHDVoelCfm5J768wx5sd6SPqyjwwgwoIOzal8Z9yQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入。

2.输入蒙文单词和附加成分时，要用-（减号）把单词与后面的附加成分连在一起输入（请参见本文附件中的附加成分表）。例如：内蒙古大学蒙古语文研究所

![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRr6iclAhS2mwQCicQJjOVGWy6wmppsqaiay2rkKc580XibE6k8LUJRQXa3w/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入方法是：orbor mqnggql-vn yehe svrgagvli-yin mqnggql hele bicg svdvlhv gajar;

3.蒙音字符a,q,v为阳性元音,e,E,o,u为阴性元音,i为中性元音。如果蒙文单词（包括连在一起的附加成分）中只有阳性元音就称为阳性词,如果只有阴性元音就称为阴性词，如果既没有阳性元音也没有阴性元音或既有阳性元音也有阴性元音就称为中性词。输入时，不管阳性元音、阴性元音在单词的什么位置（包括附加成分中）都决定整个单词的词性；

4.只有中性单词中的g,G字形受词性影响，g为阴性字形，G为阳性字形。例如：![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdIWmgZvAkQ6DwbWiaXQAUjImokYc9Wjyia5d6hZBLFlPZTmvLbjKan8TA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)和![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCd54I8BFlY7vMWcicH30pZAWg2uQ7HVDjiaz4h9SECk5BfgJro5GgkhSsA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入方法是sig和siG;

5.y代表![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCddBnibfLugulQSjTy1AsPK6tn4BrknQSfDhJ26DQTicAC5GpQycxMVicpQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)，i代表![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdRKXkutjZcT0nE433ZGyGP2qoNaWv4uOwFdTYyUkvnj2ib71iaSNhWIaA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的各种字形，但元音字符后的yi组合代表![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdlf9gYUCBWhQ6HR3I0SdfGFoCtzzhufMBOooufX7Iy1uDk5rDdYqiavg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)和![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdYorFBYrDQeEx4JnfyDVaTJWlVeibicK7DFUsn4UGibFlNAuIXU02tlJeg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)，需要输入元音后的![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WR7fbTuV2rPHan9WibgLiahJhREAW6ibaoowGuksyU4Q6icpOIqwuklQISsw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)和![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRC39z4ibUWb02Zia5YoNczTfWb0Dfsqods6RPt2rEePjUkQVcrVN3vozg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)时，![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdicnksuMobZy9cYt1FELUPHxsuRdK7BgkbNhMdb7pfo17ElW9gS34ujw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)需要用大写Y。例如：![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdEaTnibCMzTIe0oUW3huvAU78rXqy2KZ1bFfuRPm3mcE8zopUl867vnw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1),![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdAZHCN5gEuBR6dS0zb28WibrfZ5SIUB24DHaMUmgicuf7cialFqcg0cXJA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1),![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdgJr5iaGccgHnHXiaxTrufggq1ibLBmIgMVFRo1EiathuTqVQSUPDwAUichg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1),![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdVUD3IiaExUL5DiaklNA54AibOMZTSQetneCeQ7xYnVZMFO5G0XPjEVzFw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入方法是bayin_a, sayi, maYig, saYi；



6.用_a,_e输入![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdwSvdaPib7qrMV8QwLsC0afqicUwPicibnoM3ZONklzFlaVGpXia0lIt1blw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdZcKyKC5K2C7uwEHDVoelCfm5J768wx5sd6SPqyjwwgwoIOzal8Z9yQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)字形。例如：![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdEaTnibCMzTIe0oUW3huvAU78rXqy2KZ1bFfuRPm3mcE8zopUl867vnw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)，![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdmPh6wukuib373ajGrSBWddfQg54zeZ8khXZjJk7iaCwvCmRgCHjG0n3g/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入方法是bayin_a, irel_e;

7.单撇'有两个用处，一是连接输入两个词组合的人名或地名，二是词末不规则变形加一撇。例如：![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdNgg93lQDcVFRVRiac4c42NSK3bMYpELr4OMcxprYThYmukRpc5rjWSA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1),![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdUTdug3IM9jhuwWdSe6I57EC2gY5hXvA8G7o5Im9TcyfOIBuVITRstQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1),![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdEuT9gyMBADvp6JzM0ovULnj0nFxic97gemqdPLss6BeibXNTvibxQdEFw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入方法是bqyan'arbin, has'erdeni, huhe'hqta. ![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdib461jUj7hIAuicSCRaUD8u20f4ReBGPlvBKVeBaY6bH3IabficAtyibeg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1),![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdXSVYDHgicDZqPviaMdleIeG77WGarfOKCpZvlTWQfKEQoQe8I3Gtk0Gw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1),![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdFUvEic5Bcpl2esLR2ibe91twn0ibOcB1z4TT8sMGJXrbU57FJ1lxxglaw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入方法是su',kinq',fu';

8.另有不规则的字形变换或外来语用大写字符N,G,T,D输入。例如：![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdzkDjgACrRvukiaf9o01lIAkfMibVHFWriakzKtVlEfq2iazoibJVWbq1xEQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)，![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdEEj4TJjyhk9TANaNEgoZpJl7gLuBRp3Y1FaJAWDFllLkVbxyfN81eQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)，![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdDz9Qgs8sxDMib6fXP7WRKgYrDTuagPh9PYS8NasQkvA8MXTwmqH3Z1Q/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)，![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCdDXvCoWAHSmc6ftPrW5I16fD3UbS3jzaw3AcOxIVx5Ow7Wk2ibl6YeEg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)的输入方法是Gram,ciNw_a,eD,DEng;

9.把蒙文标点符号对应在适合的键位上，参见本文附件，在此不赘述。



## 二、蒙古文万码（![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCd7NzfzUQP2TuLhRpZSMicGYWJU2ZvqnuOzia4QibeR9za8nFjYia6Ia0sCg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)Hagam Mongol KQD）系统平台上蒙文读音输入方法变化之内容



传统蒙古文字形字符研究团队编制了首个团队标准（The Team Stantard） TmSd AEI768 Ver 0.1.0——《传统蒙古文信息交换与处理字形字符编码字符集》（简称TmSd《字形编码》）0.1.0版,并以此为基础开发了蒙古文万码（![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo3tcBPwsJo9brhPEM0GsibCd7NzfzUQP2TuLhRpZSMicGYWJU2ZvqnuOzia4QibeR9za8nFjYia6Ia0sCg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)Hagam Mongol KQD）系统平台，系统平台上也实现了蒙文读音输入方法。

在TmSd《字形编码》有字符![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRZU8ic9HGVqWLNKoFzFuyBmzB3qDQ1niaibCalLtuqMfZHELb2qwztNPtA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)（末形）、![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WR7K83ylP09fARnCxW2EZ0BlCzSoxnR7NrXDg96QmibFzHjHRL7fweXpQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)、![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRicSRicptLuI7RrPNODr2eGecwRlj53c1iaEVU6licGfiaHSnI8jWadpqbNw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)（末形）、![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRiaib0cWchHo7OMpxqn0CfmBTbwdmSgxF5uiaK1CeZkkZU347qzrssoswQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WR0wR3V1XmnohlFtpZfnYY59CdoN3a9cWtNW0XOuV424asJbRGrZic3dg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)、整字符![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRvRudiccnmxiaP1tzUZicYzg4ia03gVgPgHky2KdcLibicDKbyiaT3JjIBzcsw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)、![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRUf4fWnCfBVZCua4R8agchr3QzYjFDbCXR4JibOyK7BTzJyjPMt3ibgPw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)、![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRJMBBqibiacWKIaUZKuON6AEBl3M4YuQzwC9UdIxTXtC8teOQ3xcaZJzg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)、![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRJCIxAkZk1mpVSKrowxDae0wGZZUZ4qdVSevylff2daibzyEDyje9VHg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)、![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRx7gOPql6pSsHPJxIOnhgeomqyQ3gbyOmjfLZCek8oYsVbm7UblOWXQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)（末形）需要定义新的输入规则，定义规则如下：

1.用b'输入![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRZU8ic9HGVqWLNKoFzFuyBmzB3qDQ1niaibCalLtuqMfZHELb2qwztNPtA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)（末形）；

2.用h'输入![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WR7K83ylP09fARnCxW2EZ0BlCzSoxnR7NrXDg96QmibFzHjHRL7fweXpQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)；

3.用s'输入![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRicSRicptLuI7RrPNODr2eGecwRlj53c1iaEVU6licGfiaHSnI8jWadpqbNw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)（末形）；

4.用K输入![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRiaib0cWchHo7OMpxqn0CfmBTbwdmSgxF5uiaK1CeZkkZU347qzrssoswQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WR0wR3V1XmnohlFtpZfnYY59CdoN3a9cWtNW0XOuV424asJbRGrZic3dg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)；

5.用ZHi'输入整字符![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRvRudiccnmxiaP1tzUZicYzg4ia03gVgPgHky2KdcLibicDKbyiaT3JjIBzcsw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)；

6.用CHi'输入整字符![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRUf4fWnCfBVZCua4R8agchr3QzYjFDbCXR4JibOyK7BTzJyjPMt3ibgPw/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)；

7.整字符![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRJMBBqibiacWKIaUZKuON6AEBl3M4YuQzwC9UdIxTXtC8teOQ3xcaZJzg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)、![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRJCIxAkZk1mpVSKrowxDae0wGZZUZ4qdVSevylff2daibzyEDyje9VHg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)用于附加成分,用Yi和-（减号）与前一词连起来输入；

8.整字符![img](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/s4RyjEaHDo2s4mbjXBm5VefIbpAB33WRx7gOPql6pSsHPJxIOnhgeomqyQ3gbyOmjfLZCek8oYsVbm7UblOWXQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)用于词末，用单个Y输入。





